Port of https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode/pull/13218 (multi-account profile
support per provider). The original PR targeted the pre-Effect-TS codebase, so
the auth core had to be rewritten.

Adds a /profile TUI slash command to switch between profiles (with `r` to
rename), and `opencode auth profile {create,use,list,remove,rename}` CLI
subcommands. Creating new profiles is also integrated into the /connect flow:
when connecting a provider that already has credentials, it prompts for a
profile name first.

